{"tid":2102650,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香港邊度海南雞好食","createTime":"2020-07-10T15:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T06:41:22.000Z","uid":351169,"like":6,"dislike":151,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"e7e8d217ae8f6b93f8a468129a317a73a08bc0d9","tid":2102650,"uid":351169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:20:33.000Z","msg":"其實我呢就吾系十分中意食海南雞嘅<br />\n但另一半就好中意食，所以就陪太子寫字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不知不覺就試左好多間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想分享比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[url]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/85nn6jG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F85nn6jG.jpg&h=9b5e80ff&s={SIZE}\" />[/url]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Qnn6tc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Qnn6tc.png&h=e38017fd&s={SIZE}\" />呢張個境咁正系入住左酒店叫左room service<br />\n<br />\n評分如下<br />\n總體有9/10分<br />\n價錢黎講$295（仲要加一）<br />\n雖然真系好好食，扣左一分就系價錢吾親民<br />\n<br />\n海南雞系好入味，雞嘅份量都多嫁雞皮一D都吾肥，吾點醬都好有味，雞胸位吾柴系好食嘅<br />\n<br />\n到個飯呢就粒粒分明，吾會太淡味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到啲醬呢個人覺得薑容冇乜太大特別，但個辣醬真系不得了，吾知佢點整，入口系吾辣嘅，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但慢慢會麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我呢都試過午餐同晚餐去食，覺得午餐啲雞好食嘅，同埋啲雞好似啱啱浸起好鬼滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n系時候開估拉呢間系grand hyatt Hong Kong 君悅酒店咖啡廳<br />\n<br />\n啦啦啦。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家中意睇就講多幾間，全部都系自費無幫佢賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小女子第一次岀飲食post 希望多少少正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe416eea4b092a4e0fdba200c62c8451c5de3245","tid":2102650,"uid":187,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:21:21.000Z","msg":"一黎咁高級好難講啲平民飯"},{"pid":"3f9b11fa7460efed00568bce51f59bbeadc6c293","tid":2102650,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:24:45.000Z","msg":"想問下海南雞可以點入味？"},{"pid":"a4877089d1d6abab2bf264dd7633ae3060dd4f89","tid":2102650,"uid":351169,"like":1,"dislike":29,"score":-28,"quote":{"pid":"3f9b11fa7460efed00568bce51f59bbeadc6c293","tid":2102650,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:24:45.000Z","msg":"想問下海南雞可以點入味？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:31:32.000Z","msg":"我淨係識食，吾識煮喎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每間整雞都吾同嘅 ，有啲會浸雞湯、冰水和秘製滷水，雞皮爽脆入味，雞肉嫩滑。"},{"pid":"8fa91e0c01d8cadb355cd4be4aa54a7cf89d962e","tid":2102650,"uid":43983,"like":51,"dislike":3,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:38:32.000Z","msg":"三舊水一碟我仲有咩好同你比較<br />\n出返去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f47c46be0af108818a92ab9f0b69015dd9aff1","tid":2102650,"uid":25088,"like":74,"dislike":0,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:42:08.000Z","msg":"又吾又系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dda6fdc74c3307ec203e37295c41d13bed7c3af","tid":2102650,"uid":78392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:45:14.000Z","msg":"介紹下黃店啦"},{"pid":"6520dd7e5e26085875f9e7fe7152dbf030255d08","tid":2102650,"uid":218575,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:51:52.000Z","msg":"又吾又系 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c89a14210a546a373d8b977f0f4c451355e9a9","tid":2102650,"uid":54194,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:08:35.000Z