:7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T19:26:07.000Z","msg":"300蚊有呢個質素，有乜咁值得吹奏？<br />\n如果300蚊d雞都係柴嘅，佢切腹啦！<br />\n<br />\n簡單一間黃店拋磚引玉：<br />\n大角嘴大全街星洲總廚。<br />\n佢嘅海南雞飯唔柴、夠滑，飯亦夠油香且顆粒分明，最重要係佢嘅海南雞飯$70有找。"},{"pid":"31b27e135e3a441bffd0e4f8ab9c587e02160514","tid":2102650,"uid":94233,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T19:29:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OtuqmcD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOtuqmcD.gif&h=3e69e5e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb675bd771df9edf283c5058b106a5c178ac8ba2","tid":2102650,"uid":21611,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T19:48:56.000Z","msg":"元朗西菁街南香雞飯<br />\n我敢講肯撚定係全港最滑！"},{"pid":"58dec3c7be7fe82774a4c2bc6e03c94772107e71","tid":2102650,"uid":39514,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T20:37:09.000Z","msg":"2020年仲有人用5p字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af0ad8e3abefbd62fb40df4822f00f55e64bcaa","tid":2102650,"uid":13466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T20:39:25.000Z","msg":"搭單問下，呢度d人鍾意食新加坡式海南雞？定泰式海南雞？<br />\n<br />\n我鍾意新加坡式，尤其個黑醬油一絕。<br />\n反而泰式我成日覺得有陣怪味，而且d泰式辣雞醬我唔識欣賞。"},{"pid":"b8cdbf2c2b6b89a780208627b98e5f20c82ee2d1","tid":2102650,"uid":6946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"044253554ca429381a22feac619d65e1c33d8ac3","tid":2102650,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:39:17.000Z","msg":"沙田馬會公眾canteen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T20:43:22.000Z","msg":"雞脾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339655b9f251e0eb2e63e4161bae271d0221b72d","tid":2102650,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a4877089d1d6abab2bf264dd7633ae3060dd4f89","tid":2102650,"uid":351169,"like":1,"dislike":29,"score":-28,"quote":{"pid":"3f9b11fa7460efed00568