48df925662de453a9","tid":2102650,"uid":162061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T21:26:42.000Z","msg":"西灣河 太安樓 <br />\n不過依家無之前咁好食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T04:11:23.000Z","msg":"藍店不了"},{"pid":"16058be8614554c79f2f67b7942c3b09492eb8bd","tid":2102650,"uid":110495,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e7e8d217ae8f6b93f8a468129a317a73a08bc0d9","tid":2102650,"uid":351169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T15:20:33.000Z","msg":"其實我呢就吾系十分中意食海南雞嘅<br />\n但另一半就好中意食，所以就陪太子寫字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不知不覺就試左好多間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想分享比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[url]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/85nn6jG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F85nn6jG.jpg&h=9b5e80ff&s={SIZE}\" />[/url]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Qnn6tc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Qnn6tc.png&h=e38017fd&s={SIZE}\" />呢張個境咁正系入住左酒店叫左room service<br />\n<br />\n評分如下<br />\n總體有9/10分<br />\n價錢黎講$295（仲要加一）<br />\n雖然真系好好食，扣左一分就系價錢吾親民<br />\n<br />\n海南雞系好入味，雞嘅份量都多嫁雞皮一D都吾肥，吾點醬都好有味，雞胸位吾柴系好食嘅<br />\n<br />\n到個飯呢就粒粒分明，吾會太淡味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到啲醬呢個人覺得薑容冇乜太大特別，但個辣醬真系不得了，吾知佢點整，入口系吾辣嘅，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但慢慢會麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我呢都試過午餐同晚餐去食，覺得午餐啲雞好食嘅，同埋啲雞好似啱啱浸起好鬼滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n系時候開估拉呢間系grand hyatt Hong Kong 君悅酒店咖啡廳<br />\n<br />\n啦啦啦。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家中意睇就講多幾間，全部都系自費無幫佢賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小女子第一次岀飲食post 希望多少少正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T04:34:09.000Z","msg":"太安樓海南雞幾好食"},{"pid":"a5392ddda0a3f4c4fb8cc380ed8a8aca21c7ae72","tid":2102650,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T04:44:36.000Z","msg":"AC2"},{"pid":"6bdc6da94455834a33e8b038b1a28b812adb1099","tid":2102650,"uid":74113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bdef1f55dd43b7714ea54fb72b2a465cdc22bdec","tid":2102650,"uid":71824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:39:25.000Z","msg":"Chatterbox掂唔掂？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T04:47:23.000Z","msg":"唔好食 <br />\n又貴又普通"},{"pid":"670bdd1557e9f4c3c600f507ddd37db7429b6441","tid":2102650,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19cb44c893e7a7fc47d62323a3f6660015c5763a","tid":2102650,"uid":16696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0af0ad8e3abefbd62fb40df4822f00f55e64bcaa","tid":2102650,"uid":13466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T20:39:25.000Z","msg":"搭單問下，呢度d人鍾意食新加坡式海南雞？定泰式海南雞？<br />\n<br />\n我鍾意新加坡式，尤其個黑醬油一絕。<br />\n反而泰式我成日覺得有陣怪味，而且d泰式辣雞醬我唔識欣賞。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T20:49:30.000Z","msg":"我鍾意新加坡式雞 泰式醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰式雞飯好易整到好鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T06:03:54.000Z","msg":"same <br />\nmonkey雞 + 泰醬"},{"pid":"2d384bfc7c8e7dd588d7eac8d5788b047c8e2d6c","tid":2102650,"uid":37171,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T06:25:19.000Z","msg":"5p字都冇人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2043fb8b7f26c43f8f5af9f84e3e909ecd3612